data.title: ROHAN CALLS FOR AID - Third Age Total War Gameplay
data.description:
Third Age Total War Gameplay - Saruman is building a mighty army, and he is constantly raiding the lands of Rohan.  To counter the raids Rohan has sent out small patrol forces to defend their borders.  But no patrol force will be ready for what is coming after them.  Isengard is sending a massive raiding army and Rohan calls out for aid!  The Silvan Elves answer the call! But will they make it in time?  Will Rohan last?  Enjoy the Battle :D

Big Thanks to Chan for making this Scenario! 

If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
